{
  "stem": "23942.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- and, you know, and I asked-- I wasn't used to a queen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, I never heard of a queen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A queen and two princesses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were my age.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was so nice to hear such a normal-- such-- such-- such a [INAUDIBLE] for queen for [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know the history, but I-- I felt this-- this-- this great feeling of a queen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they loved her, the queen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And every-- even the Jewish-- the subjects, they had such respect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and I bought a postcard, I remember, of the queen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I brought it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't want to part with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, and anyway, I went to see the palace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I went to see a museum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They tried to-- to-- to show me a little bit of London.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Buckingham Palace.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They took me to see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Took me to see a few important sites.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I even-- I remember the one movie that I loved-- I saw the first movie, beautiful movie, that I saw was And that was an experience because they were showing Vivien Leigh.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was very-- a nice experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a beautiful movie with all the pageantry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that was a nice movie to see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It wasn't sad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it didn't remind me of sadness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And everything was slowly getting to like sort of-- getting better for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was-- every day brought me closer to-- to normal, to being normal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I even developed-- I remember, what means normal?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like children have-- I didn't experience what-- to be-- to have a childhood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lost my childhood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the first time I-- I developed a hobby in London.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started collecting stamps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's when I was first aware of geography through these stamps.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
